<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-473] Major compaction still leaves large set of files</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-473</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We did a major compaction on roughly 1000-2000 files. The disk drive had a capacity of 1.6TB. The disk usage with Cassandra was 1.1TB. I saw this error, maybe this is why compaction did not finish? Attaching system.log&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12437407">CASSANDRA-473</key>
            <summary>Major compaction still leaves large set of files</summary>
